title: Now and Then-Chris De Burghs new CD+Covers
description: Released in April 2008 through UMTV and initially only available in the UK and Eire, \&#039;Now And Then\&#039; is a brand new compilation album of Chris\&#039;s greatest hits and classic tracks. The compilation will be announced by the release of a promotional single, the duet \&#039;Live For The Day\&#039;, recorded with rising 20-year-old Lebanese star Tina Yamout.
